--==About==--
This program will browse the defined URLS in a minimized, invisible, Internet Explorer browser window. Each URL will then be opened up in its own tab. It will browse the 4 URLS for 3 minutes, close Internet Explorer, and start again using a different proxy. The use of a proxy is not required, but your IP address does not remain hidden this way.

You can go about your normal computer activities while this program is running it will not interfere with you at all.

This program is useful for sites that pay you to view advertisements. But does break most TOS, so use at your own risk. This is not an autoclicker program and does not work with those type of sites. Works with sites like LinkBucks and UCash, possibly others.
